            <span class="block text-slate-300 mt-2">The Clients You Want</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-white/90 max-w-2xl">{description}</p>
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-white font-medium mb-2">The agency pitch reality:</p>
            <p class="text-white/90 text-sm">Marketing director searching "creative agency for rebrand" visits 18 agency websites. 13 have outdated work, vague case studies, no clear process, difficult contact forms. 1 modern site with video case studies, clear results metrics (34% conversion lift), visible team, straightforward inquiry process. Guess who gets the RFP? For agencies, visible results = proven capability = hire you. Your website = 24/7 pitch deck working while you sleep.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 bg-[#F8FAFC]">
