        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-slate-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Case study with results visible: 6x more qualified RFPs</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Agency had "portfolio available on request" only. Added detailed case study with "34% conversion lift" prominently. Month 1: 6x more qualified RFPs. Results = proven = hire you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
