            <span class="text-slate-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Video case study visible: 5x more engagement</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Added 60-second case study video prominently. Month 1: 5x longer site visits, 4x more inquiries. Video = see work in action = want you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-slate-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Client testimonials visible: 53% more trust</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Added Fortune 500 client quotes with headshots prominently. Month 1: 53% more qualified inquiries. Endorsements = trust = hire you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-slate-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Process visible: 43% smoother onboarding</p>
