            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-slate-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Mobile portfolio viewing: 79% check on phones</p>
