          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-2">See how Webflow and Framer compare for agencies</p>
          <a href="/comparisons/webflow-vs-framer" class="text-slate-600 font-semibold hover:underline text-sm">Compare Webflow vs Framer â†’</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-5 border-l-4 border-slate-500 rounded-r-lg">
